{
  "page": "Aliandra Martell",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Martell\" title=\"House Martell\"><img alt=\"House Martell.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/60/House_Martell.svg/50px-House_Martell.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/60/House_Martell.svg/75px-House_Martell.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/60/House_Martell.svg/100px-House_Martell.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Princess</span><br />Aliandra Martell</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Martell\" title=\"House Martell\"><img alt=\"House Martell.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/60/House_Martell.svg/50px-House_Martell.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/60/House_Martell.svg/75px-House_Martell.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/60/House_Martell.svg/100px-House_Martell.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Princess_Aliandra_Martell_and_her_consort,_Drazenko_Rogare_by_viscardiac.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Princess Aliandra Martell and her consort, Drazenko Rogare by viscardiac.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/2d/Princess_Aliandra_Martell_and_her_consort%2C_Drazenko_Rogare_by_viscardiac.png/350px-Princess_Aliandra_Martell_and_her_consort%2C_Drazenko_Rogare_by_viscardiac.png\" width=\"350\" height=\"350\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/2d/Princess_Aliandra_Martell_and_her_consort%2C_Drazenko_Rogare_by_viscardiac.png/525px-Princess_Aliandra_Martell_and_her_consort%2C_Drazenko_Rogare_by_viscardiac.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/2d/Princess_Aliandra_Martell_and_her_consort%2C_Drazenko_Rogare_by_viscardiac.png/700px-Princess_Aliandra_Martell_and_her_consort%2C_Drazenko_Rogare_by_viscardiac.png 2x\" /></a><div>Princess Aliandra Martell and her consort, by <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://viscardiac.tumblr.com/\">viscardiac</a> ©</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Titles</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Princess_of_Dorne\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Princess of Dorne\">Princess of Dorne</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_voyage_of_alyn_oakenfist.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_voyage_of_alyn_oakenfist.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Lady_of_Sunspear\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Lady of Sunspear\">Lady of Sunspear</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_voyage_of_alyn_oakenfist.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_voyage_of_alyn_oakenfist.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Martell\" title=\"House Martell\">House Martell</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Dornishmen\" title=\"Dornishmen\">Dornishmen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_115_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">115&#160;AC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-ages_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-ages-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/136_AC\" title=\"136 AC\">136</a>–<a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_158_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">158&#160;AC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-ages_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-ages-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Father</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Qoren_Martell\" title=\"Qoren Martell\">Qoren Martell</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Spouse</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Drazenko_Rogare\" title=\"Drazenko Rogare\">Drazenko Rogare</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Lover</th><td>\nLord <a href=\"/index.php/Alyn_Velaryon\" title=\"Alyn Velaryon\">Alyn Velaryon</a> <small>(rumored)</small><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Rise_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"The Rise of the Dragon\">The Rise of the Dragon</a></i> (mentioned)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Aliandra Nymeros Martell</b> was the ruling <a href=\"/index.php/Princess_of_Dorne\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Princess of Dorne\">Princess of Dorne</a> and the head of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Martell\" title=\"House Martell\">House Nymeros Martell</a> during the reign of King <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_III_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon III Targaryen\">Aegon III Targaryen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafdorne:_dorne_against_the_dragons.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafdorne:_dorne_against_the_dragons.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Character\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Character</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Family\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Family</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Character\">Character</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Aliandra_Martell&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Character\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">See also: <a href=\"/index.php/Category:Images_of_Aliandra_Martell\" title=\"Category:Images of Aliandra Martell\">Images of Aliandra Martell</a></div>\n<p>Aliandra was a flirtatious and fiery young woman.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_voyage_of_alyn_oakenfist.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_voyage_of_alyn_oakenfist.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafdorne:_dorne_against_the_dragons.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafdorne:_dorne_against_the_dragons.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Aliandra_Martell&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The daughter of Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Qoren_Martell\" title=\"Qoren Martell\">Qoren Martell</a>, Aliandra became <a href=\"/index.php/Princess_of_Dorne\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Princess of Dorne\">Princess of Dorne</a> by the age of seventeen. She saw herself as \"the new <a href=\"/index.php/Nymeria\" title=\"Nymeria\">Nymeria</a>\"<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_hooded_hand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_hooded_hand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> and encouraged her <a href=\"/index.php/Lord\" title=\"Lord\">lords</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knights</a> to prove themselves to her by raiding in the <a href=\"/index.php/Dornish_Marches\" title=\"Dornish Marches\">Dornish Marches</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafdorne:_dorne_against_the_dragons.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafdorne:_dorne_against_the_dragons.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> Aliandra's younger brother, Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Qyle_Martell\" title=\"Qyle Martell\">Qyle</a>, was suggested as a possible husband for Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Baela_Targaryen\" title=\"Baela Targaryen\">Baela Targaryen</a>, but she wed her cousin Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Alyn_Velaryon\" title=\"Alyn Velaryon\">Alyn Velaryon</a> instead.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_hooded_hand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_hooded_hand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>In <a href=\"/index.php/133_AC\" title=\"133 AC\">133&#160;AC</a>, when Aliandra was eighteen, she met Alyn Velaryon during his first <a href=\"/index.php/Great_Voyages\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Great Voyages\">great journey</a>, when his campaign to defend the <a href=\"/index.php/Westerlands\" title=\"Westerlands\">westerlands</a> from Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Dalton_Greyjoy\" title=\"Dalton Greyjoy\">Dalton Greyjoy</a> brought him to <a href=\"/index.php/Sunspear\" title=\"Sunspear\">Sunspear</a>. The book <i><a href=\"/index.php/Bastard_Born\" title=\"Bastard Born\">Bastard Born</a></i> claims that Alyn had to provide intimate services to Aliandra before she allowed him provisions for his <a href=\"/index.php/Velaryon_fleet\" title=\"Velaryon fleet\">fleet</a>, although another biography of Alyn, <i><a href=\"/index.php/Hard_as_Oak\" title=\"Hard as Oak\">Hard as Oak</a></i>, contradicts that story.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_voyage_of_alyn_oakenfist.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_voyage_of_alyn_oakenfist.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Aliandra met Alyn again when he returned from the <a href=\"/index.php/Sunset_Sea\" title=\"Sunset Sea\">Sunset Sea</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Drazenko_Rogare\" title=\"Drazenko Rogare\">Drazenko Rogare</a>, a <a href=\"/index.php/Lys\" title=\"Lys\">Lysene</a> envoy, informed the Oakenfist that Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Viserys_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Viserys II Targaryen\">Viserys Targaryen</a> was a captive of his brother, <a href=\"/index.php/Lysandro_Rogare\" title=\"Lysandro Rogare\">Lysandro Rogare</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_voyage_of_alyn_oakenfist.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_voyage_of_alyn_oakenfist.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> Aliandra showed great favor to Alyn during his visits.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafdorne:_dorne_against_the_dragons.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafdorne:_dorne_against_the_dragons.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> Alyn's wife, Baela Targaryen, disliked hearing about Aliandra.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Aliandra was one of the greatest beneficiaries of the <a href=\"/index.php/Daughters%27_War\" title=\"Daughters&#39; War\">Daughters' War</a>, with <a href=\"/index.php/Dorne\" title=\"Dorne\">Dorne</a> taking dominion over most of the <a href=\"/index.php/Stepstones\" title=\"Stepstones\">Stepstones</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> During the <a href=\"/index.php/Lysene_Spring\" title=\"Lysene Spring\">Lysene Spring</a>, Aliandra married Drazenko and named him <a href=\"/index.php/Prince_Consort_of_Dorne\" title=\"Prince Consort of Dorne\">Prince Consort of Dorne</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_the_Stepstones\" title=\"Lord of the Stepstones\">Lord of the Stepstones</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_free_cities:_the_quarrelsome_daughters:_myr.2C_lys.2C_and_tyrosh.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_free_cities:_the_quarrelsome_daughters:_myr.2C_lys.2C_and_tyrosh.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup> When Drazenko suspiciously choked to death on bacon in <a href=\"/index.php/135_AC\" title=\"135 AC\">135&#160;AC</a>, his death was attributed by some to the <a href=\"/index.php/Faceless_Men\" title=\"Faceless Men\">Faceless Men</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Braavos\" title=\"Braavos\">Braavos</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Aliandra_Martell&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>It is unknown whether Aliandra and Drazenko had offspring, and whether said offspring continued <a href=\"/index.php/House_Martell\" title=\"House Martell\">House Martell</a>.\n</p>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;font: 90% sans-serif;\">\n<tbody><tr align=\"center\"><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\"><a href=\"/index.php/Qoren_Martell\" title=\"Qoren Martell\">Qoren</a></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\">Unknown<br />wife</td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td></tr><tr align=\"center\"><td style=\"border-right:1px solid black\"><div style=\"width:1em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td><div style=\"width:1em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td></tr>\n<tr align=\"center\"><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px se